highlights.text: “Stay with Me” by Huh Gak is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Hong Kong at #84.
Sabrina Carpenter has the most spots on Viral Songs Hong Kong. “Tears” is the highest at #23.
“用背脊唱情歌” by Gareth.T has been on Viral Songs Hong Kong the longest, at 91 days straight.
“Mr. "Broken Heart"” by YOUYA is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Hong Kong, up 39 spots at #58.
